TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;
$a1 = random(3,7,1);
$b1 = random(1,5,1);
$c1 = random(2,6,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
If \( \ln( $a1 x + $c1 )= $b1 \), then \( x = \) \{ans_rule(20) \}.
EOT

$ans = (exp($b1)-$c1) /$a1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

